Step 5: Git mergetool integration (--local/--base/--remote/--result CLI)

New module:
  - git/mergetool.rs: CLI argument parsing, env var helpers, 5 tests
  - git/mod.rs: module exports

Changes:
  - main.rs: detects mergetool args, sets env vars, launches GUI
  - lib.rs: auto-opens result file in mergetool mode via pre-loaded session
